<plot>The Detective Jack is bound with a missile guidance device by Domingues. This is an impossible task. 1.To cancel the missile guidance, Jack has to get 4 digit code. This code is written on the statue of liberty's forehead in Las Vegas which is 230miles from him. 2. The missile guidance device is itself a time bomb. To unlock this device, he has to get a key which is on the roof of the Nakatomi building. Jack is chased by a Tomahawk which is followed by 10 patriot missiles. Time limit is only 17 minutes. Jack runs around Los Angeles to diffuse the missile guidance and gets into trouble with a German Terrorist, Mad Dentist, Animal Abuser and LAPD. They chase Jack without knowing about the missile. Finally the missile explodes with a huge mushroom cloud on the Nakatomi Building. They are blown into the sky !</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?203696</url></doc>
